What do you mean "talk about it later"?

285
00:11:59,320 --> 00:12:00,790
Didn't you say we would decide today?

286
00:12:02,000 --> 00:12:02,790
Hui.

287
00:12:05,080 --> 00:12:05,870
Hui.

288
00:12:07,630 --> 00:12:09,720
Why are you calling me back like this?

289
00:12:09,960 --> 00:12:11,590
Couldn't you have just told me over the phone?

290
00:12:12,240 --> 00:12:13,630
I have a lot of things to handle.

291
00:12:14,080 --> 00:12:14,700
Damin,

292
00:12:15,910 --> 00:12:16,910
we don't know

293
00:12:16,910 --> 00:12:18,320
how long this lawsuit will drag on.

294
00:12:18,750 --> 00:12:21,360
Those funds are just sitting idle with you.

295
00:12:21,630 --> 00:12:23,200
We can't lend them out either.

296
00:12:23,510 --> 00:12:24,390
Han gave us

297
00:12:24,390 --> 00:12:25,600
an idea.

298
00:12:26,030 --> 00:12:27,270
He suggested that I open a new company

299
00:12:27,270 --> 00:12:28,450
under my cousin's name.

300
00:12:28,600 --> 00:12:29,160
Hurry up

301
00:12:29,360 --> 00:12:30,030
and transfer that money

302
00:12:30,030 --> 00:12:31,480
to our new company right away.

303
00:12:35,360 --> 00:12:36,150
Oh, that?

304
00:12:37,630 --> 00:12:38,250
Alright.

305
00:12:39,030 --> 00:12:39,620
Hui,

306
00:12:40,580 --> 00:12:41,390
you're right.

307
00:12:43,000 --> 00:12:44,020
I can't just

308
00:12:44,650 --> 00:12:46,960
let all that money sit there idly.

309
00:12:47,080 --> 00:12:47,790
Right?

310
00:12:47,870 --> 00:12:49,550
It's not that I'm afraid of being stolen, but I'm afraid of being targeted.

311
00:12:50,080 --> 00:12:51,790
I'm also concerned about its safety.

312
00:12:52,390 --> 00:12:55,740
So, I invested it.

313
00:12:55,970 --> 00:12:57,550
And they're all long-term investments.

314
00:12:57,550 --> 00:12:59,840
The money can't be withdrawn for a while.

315
00:13:02,860 --> 00:13:03,670
Just this?

316
00:13:05,700 --> 00:13:07,950
You could have just told me this over the phone.

317
00:13:07,970 --> 00:13:09,000
I have a lot on my plate.

318
00:13:09,000 --> 00:13:10,000
Alright, I'm leaving now.

319
00:13:10,790 --> 00:13:11,600
Hold it!

320
00:13:12,890 --> 00:13:13,540
What's wrong?

321
00:13:17,390 --> 00:13:18,910
Han was right about you.

322
00:13:19,020 --> 00:13:19,570
Han...

323
00:13:20,150 --> 00:13:20,750
Han...

324
00:13:21,870 --> 00:13:22,790
What did he say?

325
00:13:30,510 --> 00:13:31,320
Zhou Damin,

326
00:13:32,430 --> 00:13:33,630
you have someone else.

327
00:13:33,940 --> 00:13:35,690
Don't worry about whether I have someone else or not.

328
00:13:35,720 --> 00:13:36,120
Right now...

329
00:13:36,150 --> 00:13:37,110
Let me tell you,

330
00:13:37,270 --> 00:13:38,630
don't try to pull any tricks on me.

331
00:13:38,910 --> 00:13:40,090
That money is mine.

332
00:13:40,120 --> 00:13:41,450
You have to transfer it back to me.

333
00:13:41,750 --> 00:13:42,800
Remember this,

334
00:13:42,820 --> 00:13:43,940
the divorce was fake.

335
00:13:43,970 --> 00:13:45,510
The property division was also fake.

336
00:13:45,510 --> 00:13:46,790
You need to transfer the money back to me.

337
00:13:46,790 --> 00:13:47,910
It's my money.

338
00:13:47,910 --> 00:13:49,000
Otherwise, I'll sue you.

339
00:13:49,000 --> 00:13:49,920
I'll sue you.

340
00:13:49,940 --> 00:13:50,730
You've made me...

341
00:13:51,880 --> 00:13:53,160
He Qiaohui, that's enough!

342
00:13:53,510 --> 00:13:55,560
Look at you now, you're like a shrew.

343
00:13:55,670 --> 00:13:56,630
I'm curious,

344
00:13:56,630 --> 00:13:58,600
how did I endure you for so many years?

345
00:13:59,080 --> 00:14:00,340
We're already divorced.

346
00:14:01,120 --> 00:14:03,480
You mentioned the property division agreement just now.

347
00:14:03,480 --> 00:14:05,320
You read it and agreed to it before,

348
00:14:05,320 --> 00:14:06,030
right?

349
00:14:06,480 --> 00:14:07,160
From now on,

350
00:14:07,510 --> 00:14:10,000
each will follow their own path.

351
00:14:10,120 --> 00:14:11,880
Don't come looking for me again, okay?

352
00:14:12,200 --> 00:14:13,590
Please, goodbye.

353
00:14:13,960 --> 00:14:14,960
That's not true!

354
00:14:15,640 --> 00:14:17,010
Come back here!

355
00:14:17,440 --> 00:14:18,360
You're a shrew!

356
00:14:18,390 --> 00:14:19,510
Get back here!

357
00:14:43,440 --> 00:14:44,440
Is it because

358
00:14:44,600 --> 00:14:45,720
I'm getting older or what?

359
00:14:45,750 --> 00:14:47,490
My shoulders hurt just from stretching.

360
00:14:47,590 --> 00:14:48,780
You're so delicate.

361
00:14:50,360 --> 00:14:51,510
Let me drink some water.

362
00:14:53,600 --> 00:14:54,250
Shuo,

363
00:14:55,030 --> 00:14:55,960
let me tell you something.

364
00:14:57,000 --> 00:14:58,150
I have a new case.

365
00:14:58,510 --> 00:14:59,840
A couple is getting a divorce.

366
00:15:00,630 --> 00:15:02,200
The man came to me,

367
00:15:02,720 --> 00:15:04,330
but I can't even bear to talk to him.

368
00:15:04,510 --> 00:15:06,750
I think you should come and help me guide him.

369
00:15:06,750 --> 00:15:08,000
Why can't you bear to talk to him?

370
00:15:09,590 --> 00:15:11,550
He's short of money and morality.

371
00:15:13,180 --> 00:15:15,050
You only think of me now?

372
00:15:16,320 --> 00:15:17,790
Did you take this case yourself

373
00:15:17,790 --> 00:15:19,000
and are afraid of being condemned by your conscience?

374
00:15:19,000 --> 00:15:19,960
So you called me

375
00:15:20,150 --> 00:15:22,600
to shift your moral burden onto me, right?

376
00:15:23,000 --> 00:15:23,960
Then you can feel at ease

377
00:15:23,960 --> 00:15:25,320
collecting your agency fee, huh?

378
00:15:25,320 --> 00:15:26,150
No.

379
00:15:26,150 --> 00:15:27,010
To be honest,

380
00:15:27,260 --> 00:15:28,620
I've wanted to learn from you for so many years.

381
00:15:28,650 --> 00:15:30,410
When you were a lawyer,

382
00:15:30,430 --> 00:15:31,190
you didn't have a conscience,

383
00:15:31,220 --> 00:15:32,910
but I really can't learn that from you.

384
00:15:33,440 --> 00:15:34,440
I'm too upright.

385
00:15:34,440 --> 00:15:36,440
I can't help but feel uneasy at crucial moments.

386
00:15:36,520 --> 00:15:37,780
Come here and take a look at this.

387
00:15:50,000 --> 00:15:51,050
It's interesting.

388
00:15:51,790 --> 00:15:52,630
Why are you laughing?

389
00:15:53,600 --> 00:15:54,630
Isn't it a coincidence?

390
00:15:54,940 --> 00:15:56,000
I have a case too.

391
00:15:56,750 --> 00:15:57,600
The client who came to me

392
00:15:57,600 --> 00:15:58,600
is a woman.

393
00:15:59,200 --> 00:16:00,710
She's very wealthy and kind.

394
00:16:08,300 --> 00:16:09,410
This is interesting.

395
00:16:10,510 --> 00:16:12,150
The two clients who came to us are a couple.

396
00:16:12,150 --> 00:16:13,240
What a coincidence!

397
00:16:14,080 --> 00:16:15,930
The man wants to sue the woman.

398
00:16:16,150 --> 00:16:17,080
It's the woman's money.

399
00:16:17,080 --> 00:16:18,960
I guess they won't be together for much longer.

400
00:16:19,200 --> 00:16:20,000
But

401
00:16:20,910 --> 00:16:22,320
judging from these materials,

402
00:16:22,670 --> 00:16:24,200
the woman is definitely in the right.

403
00:16:25,090 --> 00:16:26,850
There's not much point in dragging this lawsuit out.

404
00:16:28,870 --> 00:16:29,500
Xue,

405
00:16:30,000 --> 00:16:30,750
how about this?

406
00:16:30,750 --> 00:16:32,390
Let's choose a more challenging case

407
00:16:32,630 --> 00:16:34,220
and represent the man?

408
00:16:35,500 --> 00:16:36,620
Are you crazy?

409
00:16:37,240 --> 00:16:38,150
The woman is rich.

410
00:16:38,170 --> 00:16:39,390
Why bother with the man?

411
00:16:39,790 --> 00:16:41,600
That's why they call me Unscrupulous Cheng.

412
00:16:42,480 --> 00:16:44,630
I want to represent this unscrupulous husband.

413
00:16:44,630 --> 00:16:45,440
I've made up my mind.

414
00:16:45,750 --> 00:16:47,020
It's up to you.

415
00:16:47,140 --> 00:16:48,590
You negotiate a higher legal fee for me.

416
00:16:49,960 --> 00:16:50,480
Here.

417
00:16:51,840 --> 00:16:54,480
What about the woman's case?

418
00:16:58,160 --> 00:16:59,190
Pass it on to Luo Yingzi.

419
00:17:00,240 --> 00:17:01,240
So you're using this case

420
00:17:01,240 --> 00:17:03,570
to curry favor with her?

421
00:17:03,720 --> 00:17:05,920
Yinghua Law Firm is short of cases anyway.

422
00:17:05,920 --> 00:17:07,780
I took a case from her before,

423
00:17:08,050 --> 00:17:09,420
so I can return the favor this time.

424
00:17:09,480 --> 00:17:11,349
Then let's stick to our old rule.

425
00:17:11,460 --> 00:17:12,980
Seventy-thirty split, you take seventy and I take thirty.

426
00:17:13,200 --> 00:17:14,640
Seventy-thirty won't work this time.

427
00:17:14,660 --> 00:17:15,700
How about eighty-twenty? Eighty-twenty.

428
00:17:16,069 --> 00:17:18,030
I'm not doing as well as before.

429
00:17:18,050 --> 00:17:19,099
I have an assistant now,

430
00:17:19,130 --> 00:17:20,280
and I have to pay him.

431
00:17:20,310 --> 00:17:21,849
An assistant? Where did he come from?

432
00:17:21,990 --> 00:17:23,400
Liangcheng Law Firm assigned him to me.

433
00:17:23,720 --> 00:17:24,760
Fang Lihong's nephew.

434
00:17:25,400 --> 00:17:26,349
He's not an assistant.

435
00:17:26,349 --> 00:17:27,750
He's just there to keep an eye on you.

436
00:17:28,130 --> 00:17:29,330
Why would he keep an eye on me?

437
00:17:29,430 --> 00:17:30,560
I'm not afraid of him.

438
00:17:31,200 --> 00:17:31,920
I don't care about that.

439
00:17:31,920 --> 00:17:33,400
Our rule is our rule.

440
00:17:33,400 --> 00:17:34,070
It's still seventy-thirty.

441
00:17:34,070 --> 00:17:35,230
That's Fang Lihong's nephew.

442
00:17:35,260 --> 00:17:36,240
Tell Fang Lihong to pay for her nephew.

443
00:17:36,240 --> 00:17:37,440
It's not my problem.

444
00:17:37,460 --> 00:17:38,760
Come on, Xue.

445
00:17:38,790 --> 00:17:39,920
Why should I feel embarrassed?

446
00:17:39,920 --> 00:17:40,680
Let's play another round.

447
00:17:41,250 --> 00:17:42,290
Eighty-twenty.

448
00:17:42,600 --> 00:17:43,980
If you win, it's seventy-thirty.

449
00:17:44,010 --> 00:17:45,120
If I win, it's eighty-twenty.

450
00:17:53,140 --> 00:17:55,650
[Jingbei Yinghua Law Firm]

451
00:18:16,510 --> 00:18:18,480
The opposing party just wants to delay time

452
00:18:18,480 --> 00:18:20,900
and transfer assets to avoid debt.

453
00:18:20,960 --> 00:18:22,070
Even if the court eventually finds out

454
00:18:22,070 --> 00:18:23,640
that their divorce was fake,

455
00:18:23,640 --> 00:18:25,400
if Zhou Damin has already

456
00:18:25,400 --> 00:18:26,700
transferred all the assets,

457
00:18:26,830 --> 00:18:28,680
it will be difficult to trace the flow of those assets.

458
00:18:28,710 --> 00:18:30,750
Enforcing the judgment will also be challenging.

459
00:18:31,070 --> 00:18:32,550
So our top priority now

460
00:18:32,580 --> 00:18:34,670
is to find a way to stop them as soon as possible.

461
00:18:36,300 --> 00:18:36,950
Yingzi,

462
00:18:37,830 --> 00:18:39,640
who is Zhou Damin's divorce lawyer?

463
00:18:39,880 --> 00:18:41,830
It's Chen Shuo's old partner,

464
00:18:41,830 --> 00:18:43,400
Xue from Dazheng Law Firm.

465
00:18:43,960 --> 00:18:44,790
Right, Xia Shu,

466
00:18:45,030 --> 00:18:46,620
we've already talked to the judge.

467
00:18:46,880 --> 00:18:48,920
The judge agreed to make a ruling as soon as possible.

468
00:18:48,950 --> 00:18:50,270
So your task now

469
00:18:50,350 --> 00:18:51,930
is to closely monitor the court

470
00:18:51,950 --> 00:18:53,090
and ensure the ruling is issued promptly.

471
00:18:53,120 --> 00:18:54,440
Then urge the court

472
00:18:54,480 --> 00:18:55,750
to serve the ruling

473
00:18:55,750 --> 00:18:57,550
on the opposing party as soon as possible.

474
00:18:57,550 --> 00:18:57,840
Okay.

475
00:18:57,970 --> 00:18:59,690
They will definitely appeal.

476
00:18:59,750 --> 00:19:00,640
But it's fine.

477
00:19:00,720 --> 00:19:03,110
We'll urge the second-instance court to hold the hearing as soon as possible.

478
00:19:04,280 --> 00:19:05,130
What can we do?

479
00:19:05,160 --> 00:19:06,960
We're dealing with a bunch of rogues.

480
00:19:06,980 --> 00:19:08,340
We have to play along with them.

481
00:19:10,270 --> 00:19:10,870
I'm leaving.

482
00:19:16,590 --> 00:19:18,590
Maybe we don't have to do anything this time.

483
00:19:18,920 --> 00:19:20,410
They might start fighting among themselves.

484
00:19:21,030 --> 00:19:22,030
What do you mean?

485
00:19:23,830 --> 00:19:25,240
Think about it. How could it be such a coincidence?

486
00:19:26,520 --> 00:19:28,850
How could He Qiaohui's husband's divorce case

487
00:19:29,350 --> 00:19:31,500
end up in Xue's hands?

488
00:19:32,110 --> 00:19:33,440
That's no coincidence.

489
00:19:33,440 --> 00:19:35,640
It's a bad idea suggested by Chen Shuo.

490
00:19:37,070 --> 00:19:38,270
Is it really a bad idea?

491
00:19:39,240 --> 00:19:41,310
We've met He Qiaohui and her husband.

492
00:19:42,150 --> 00:19:44,350
He Qiaohui's husband knows she can't escape repaying the debt.

493
00:19:44,940 --> 00:19:45,880
Was the divorce

494
00:19:46,510 --> 00:19:47,530
really fake?

495
00:19:47,830 --> 00:19:49,590
So you're saying

496
00:19:49,890 --> 00:19:52,060
He Qiaohui originally planned a fake divorce,

497
00:19:52,310 --> 00:19:53,220
but her husband

498
00:19:53,250 --> 00:19:54,840
wanted to make it real while he had the chance?

499
00:19:55,070 --> 00:19:56,590
There's no turning a fake divorce into a real one.

500
00:19:56,790 --> 00:19:58,030
Once the paperwork is done,

501
00:19:58,030 --> 00:19:59,180
the divorce is real.

502
00:20:00,110 --> 00:20:02,350
When the court rules that He Qiaohui has to repay the debt,

503
00:20:03,790 --> 00:20:06,090
do you think her husband will remarry her?

504
00:20:06,550 --> 00:20:08,400
If He Qiaohui understands this,

505
00:20:08,680 --> 00:20:10,120
will she let her husband off easily?

506
00:20:10,480 --> 00:20:13,000
Did Chen Shuo come up with this bad idea

507
00:20:13,680 --> 00:20:14,750
after thinking through

508
00:20:14,750 --> 00:20:16,160
what would happen in the future?

509
00:20:17,190 --> 00:20:18,310
But why would he do it this way?

510
00:20:18,560 --> 00:20:20,030
Don't you know?

511
00:20:20,960 --> 00:20:21,750
I don't know.

512
00:20:24,000 --> 00:20:24,680
Alright.

513
00:20:24,750 --> 00:20:26,790
Since you've assigned this case to Xia Shu,

514
00:20:26,790 --> 00:20:27,790
let her handle it.

515
00:20:28,160 --> 00:20:29,740
We're bored anyway.

516
00:20:30,070 --> 00:20:31,640
I have a small case on my hands.

517
00:20:31,720 --> 00:20:32,790
Why don't we take it?

518
00:20:33,310 --> 00:20:34,180
What kind of case?

519
00:20:34,680 --> 00:20:35,720
A divorce case.

520
00:20:35,970 --> 00:20:37,470
It was referred by Tian from Liangcheng Law Firm.

521
00:20:38,060 --> 00:20:39,950
He wants a 20% referral fee.

522
00:20:40,350 --> 00:20:41,200
No way.

523
00:20:41,960 --> 00:20:44,070
Just look at Tian's face.

524
00:20:44,440 --> 00:20:46,160
He looks like a loser.

525
00:20:46,590 --> 00:20:47,400
Qiu Hua.

526
00:20:47,550 --> 00:20:49,070
We managed to get

527
00:20:49,070 --> 00:20:51,200
a death penalty case remanded.

528
00:20:51,500 --> 00:20:52,740
Have we really sunk so low

529
00:20:52,790 --> 00:20:54,610
that we have to take on divorce cases now?

530
00:20:54,630 --> 00:20:55,460
Don't take it.

531
00:20:55,550 --> 00:20:56,160
Let me tell you,

532
00:20:56,160 --> 00:20:57,920
we won't take any case with a claim amount less than one million

533
00:20:57,920 --> 00:20:58,790
from now on.

534
00:20:59,830 --> 00:21:00,790
Really not taking it?

535
00:21:01,920 --> 00:21:03,720
The opposing lawyer is Chen Shuo.

536
00:21:05,070 --> 00:21:05,880
Chen Shuo?

537
00:21:07,000 --> 00:21:07,590
Well.

538
00:21:09,050 --> 00:21:10,290
Has Chen Shuo really sunk so low

539
00:21:10,430 --> 00:21:12,980
that he's taking on cases like this?

540
00:21:13,060 --> 00:21:14,140
I don't know about that.

541
00:21:14,750 --> 00:21:16,440
But it says he's the representing lawyer

542
00:21:16,440 --> 00:21:17,350
on the opposing side.

543
00:21:18,790 --> 00:21:19,610
Think about it.

544
00:21:23,000 --> 00:21:24,130
Interesting.

545
00:21:25,030 --> 00:21:25,880
I bet

546
00:21:25,880 --> 00:21:28,400
if Luo Yingzi hears she's going up against me,

547
00:21:28,680 --> 00:21:30,030
she'll take the case in a heartbeat.

548
00:21:30,030 --> 00:21:30,650
Do you believe me?

549
00:21:31,700 --> 00:21:33,350
She'd love the chance to get back at me.

550
00:21:33,380 --> 00:21:35,140
Alright, I'll take it.

551
00:21:37,340 --> 00:21:38,420
I don't believe it.

552
00:21:38,920 --> 00:21:40,590
I must fight with you until you admit defeat.

553
00:21:39,440 --> 00:21:48,390
[Yinghua Law Firm, Luo Yingzi, Partner]

554
00:21:51,590 --> 00:21:52,200
Yingzi.

555
00:21:52,790 --> 00:21:53,720
Ms. Jiao is here.

556
00:21:55,670 --> 00:21:57,560
Ms. Jiao, this is Ms. Luo.

557
00:21:57,940 --> 00:21:59,480
Hello, I'm Luo Yingzi.

558
00:21:59,510 --> 00:22:00,320
Hello.

559
00:22:00,130 --> 00:22:02,470
[Defendant Client, Jiao Yanling]

560
00:22:00,450 --> 00:22:01,830
Sorry for troubling you.

561
00:22:01,830 --> 00:22:03,930
No trouble at all. Let's go inside and talk.

562
00:22:03,960 --> 00:22:04,440
Please come in.

563
00:22:04,460 --> 00:22:04,920
Okay.

564
00:22:09,030 --> 00:22:10,720
Hello. I'm Chen Shuo.

