663
00:25:38,470 --> 00:25:39,910
When we were going up the stairs,

664
00:25:39,940 --> 00:25:41,580
he reached out

665
00:25:41,880 --> 00:25:43,190
to help me.

666
00:25:43,220 --> 00:25:44,830
At that moment,

667
00:25:46,280 --> 00:25:47,890
