723
00:28:13,280 --> 00:28:16,530
Where did he go?

724
00:28:16,790 --> 00:28:18,920
Later, I heard from him

725
00:28:19,200 --> 00:28:22,200
that he went to Guangdong with friends.

726
00:28:23,290 --> 00:28:24,620
I got his phone number,

727
00:28:24,650 --> 00:28:26,040
so I called him.

728
00:28:26,790 --> 00:28:29,160
I kept calling him, but he didn't answer.

729
00:28:29,160 --> 00:28:31,320
And eventually, he changed his number.

730
00:28:32,320 --> 00:28:34,370
When the child was ten months old,

731
00:28:35,070 --> 00:28:37,380
I got his exact address

732
00:28:37,550 --> 00:28:38,350
in Guangdong.

733
00:28:38,350 --> 00:28:40,090
I rushed there with the child.

734
00:28:41,070 --> 00:28:43,590
I remember waiting downstairs that day,

735
00:28:43,610 --> 00:28:44,610
while he was upstairs

736
00:28:45,120 --> 00:28:46,200
and wouldn't come down.

737
00:28:48,030 --> 00:28:49,590
I waited all day,

738
00:28:51,480 --> 00:28:53,860
and then he climbed onto the roof and ran away.

739
00:28:55,410 --> 00:28:56,730
