763
00:29:38,910 --> 00:29:39,740
I played around.

764
00:29:40,200 --> 00:29:41,440
I'm born to enjoy playing.

765
00:29:42,660 --> 00:29:43,620
Over the years,

766
00:29:44,720 --> 00:29:46,670
